ー牛乳"]}, {"box": [548, 1331, 575, 1521], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21, "lines_coords": [[[550.0, 1334.0], [571.0, 1334.0], [571.0, 1517.0], [550.0, 1517.0]]], "lines": ["放課後のししま。"]}], "img_path": "053.png"}, {"version": "0.2.0-beta.6", "img_width": 1100, "img_height": 1600, "blocks": [{"box": [601, 517, 693, 725], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27, "lines_coords": [[[660.0, 518.0], [693.0, 518.0], [693.0, 626.0], [660.0, 626.0]], [[631.0, 517.0], [657.0, 517.0], [660.0, 723.0], [634.0, 723.0]], [[603.0, 521.0], [625.0, 521.0], [625.0, 701.0], [603.0, 701.0]]], "lines": ["レンタル", "ビテオショップの", "ワゴンセールと"]}, {"box": [406, 515, 499, 736], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28, "lines_coords": [[[473.0, 521.0], [495.0, 521.0], [495.0, 698.0], [473.0, 698.0]], [[431.0, 517.0], [467.0, 515.0], [470.0, 598.0], [434.0, 600.0]], [[406.0, 518.0], [432.0, 518.0], [432.0, 731.0], [406.0, 731.0]]], "lines": ["スピーカーから", "流れる", "クリスマスソング。"]}, {"box": [492, 1309, 550, 1515], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26, "lines_coords": [[[523.0, 1310.0], [550.0, 1310.0], [550.0, 1514.0], [523.0, 1514.0]], [[492.0, 1310.0], [518.0, 1310.0], [518.0, 1446.0], [492.0, 1446.0]]], "lines": ["１ＰＬＡＹ５０円の", "格闘ゲーム。"]}], "img_path": "054.png"}, {"version": "0.2.0-beta.6", "img_width": 1100, "img_height": 1600, "blocks": [{"box": [629, 500, 688, 636], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21, "lines_coords": [[[662.0, 503.0], [684.0, 503.0], [684.0, 575.0], [662.0, 575.0]], [[631.0, 503.0], [651.0, 503.0], [651.0, 631.0], [631.0, 631.0]]], "lines": ["即走の", "街の喧曝と"]}, {"box": [375, 499, 432, 690], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21, "lines_coords": [[[407.0, 504.0], [429.0, 504.0], [429.0, 600.0], [407.0, 600.0]], [[376.0, 501.0], [396.0, 501.0], [396.0, 681.0], [376.0, 681.0]]], "lines": ["急き足で", "過き去ってゆく"]}, {"box": [528, 1311, 557, 1450], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22, "lines_coords": [[[531.0, 1317.0], [553.0, 1317.0], [553.0, 1442.0], [531.0, 1442.0]]], "lines": ["〈人〉"]}], "img_path": "055.png"}, {"version":