4.0, 1048.0]]], "lines": ["．．．ねぇ！！"]}, {"box": [609, 1046, 689, 1189], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26, "lines_coords": [[[660.0, 1046.0], [689.0, 1046.0], [689.0, 1168.0], [660.0, 1168.0]], [[635.0, 1050.0], [657.0, 1050.0], [657.0, 1143.0], [635.0, 1143.0]], [[609.0, 1050.0], [631.0, 1050.0], [631.0, 1189.0], [609.0, 1189.0]]], "lines": ["雄一くんも", "なんとか", "言ってーー！？"]}, {"box": [139, 768, 165, 900], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24, "lines_coords": [[[139.0, 768.0], [165.0, 768.0], [165.0, 900.0], [139.0, 900.0]]], "lines": ["う〜〜ん．．．"]}, {"box": [126, 1051, 193, 1081], "vertical": false, "font_size": 30, "lines_coords": [[[126.0, 1051.0], [193.0, 1051.0], [193.0, 1081.0], [126.0, 1081.0]]], "lines": ["ＯＫ！！"]}, {"box": [463, 1339, 596, 1429], "vertical": false, "font_size": 23, "lines_coords": [[[467.0, 1339.0], [557.0, 1339.0], [557.0, 1365.0], [467.0, 1365.0]], [[468.0, 1375.0], [590.0, 1375.0], [590.0, 1396.0], [468.0, 1396.0]], [[467.0, 1406.0], [567.0, 1403.0], [567.0, 1425.0], [467.0, 1428.0]]], "lines": ["Ｉｎｐｌｌｏｄ", "Ｓｔｒｏｎｄｏｒｄ", "．．．"]}], "img_path": "131.png"}, {"version": "0.2.0-beta.6", "img_width": 1100, "img_height": 1600, "blocks": [{"box": [892, 96, 1016, 282], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21, "lines_coords": [[[995.0, 98.0], [1015.0, 98.0], [1015.0, 223.0], [995.0, 223.0]], [[967.0, 96.0], [989.0, 96.0], [989.0, 240.0], [967.0, 240.0]], [[942.0, 96.0], [964.0, 96.0], [965.0, 282.0], [943.0, 282.0]], [[918.0, 96.0], [940.0, 96.0], [940.0, 221.0], [918.0, 221.0]], [[892.0, 96.0], [912.0, 96.0], [912.0, 240.0], [892.0, 240.0]]], "lines": ["．．．確かに私も", "プンプン一人で", "あの部屋あの家賃は", "どうかなって", "思ってたけど．．"]}, {"box": [523, 265, 650, 412], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21, "lines_coords": [[[628.0, 265.0], [650.0, 265.0], [650.0, 409.0], [628.0, 409.0]], [[601.0, 265.0], [623.0, 265.0], [623.0, 410.0], [601.0, 410.0]], [[576.0, 267.0], [598.0, 267.0], [598.0, 392.0], [576.0, 392.0]], [[550.0, 267.0], [571.0, 267.0], [571.0, 392.0], [550.0, 392.0]], [[523.0, 265.0], [543.0, 265.0], [543.0, 410.0], [523.0, 410.0]]], "lines": ["場所にこだわら", "ないんだったら", "大船に来れば", "いいって私は", "考えてたから．．．"]}, {"box": [357, 140, 468, 282], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25, "lines_coords": [[[435.0, 140.0], [468.0, 140.0], [468.0, 225.0], [435.0, 225.0]], [[412.0, 143.0], [434.0, 143.0], [434.0, 281.0], [412.0, 281.0]], [[382.0, 142.0], [406.0, 142.0], [407.0, 282.0], [384.0, 282.0]], [[357.0, 143.0], [379.0, 143.0], [379.0, 282.0], [357.0, 282.0]]], "lines": ["．．．コレ、", "お義姉さんの", "貯金入ってる", "通帳でしょ？"]}, {"box": [115, 298, 189, 464], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21, "lines_coords": [[[167.0, 298.0], [189.0, 298.0], [189.0, 423.0], [167.0, 423.0]], [[142.0, 300.0], [162.0, 300.0], [162.0, 464.0], [142.0, 464.0]], [[115.0, 298.0], [135.0, 298.0], [135.0, 445.0], [115.0, 445.0]]], "lines": ["まだバイトも", "ちゃんと決まって", "ないのにサァ．．．"]}, {"box": [553, 589, 579, 684], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26, "lines_coords": [[[553.0, 589.0], [579.0, 589.0], [579.0, 684.0], [553.0, 684.0]]], "lines": ["．．．あれ？"]}, {"box": [103, 504, 179, 665], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21, "lines_coords": [[[157.0, 506.0], [179.0, 506.0], [179.0, 643.0], [157.0, 643.0]], [[126.0, 504.0], [148.0, 504.0], [151.0, 665.0], [129.0, 665.0]], [[103.0, 506.0], [125.0, 506.0], [125.0, 621.0], [103.0, 621.0]]], "lines": ["ホントに私が", "預かっちゃって", "いいのね？"]}, {"box": [975, 1058, 1001, 1186], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22, "lines_coords": [[[978.0, 1059.0], [1000.0, 1059.0], [1000.0, 1185.0], [978.0, 1185.0]]], "lines": ["．．．大丈夫？"]}, {"box": [657, 1404, 720, 1535], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30, "lines_coords": [[[684.0, 1404.0], [720.0, 1404.0], [720.0, 1465.0], [684.0, 1465.0]], [[657.0, 1407.0], [681.0, 1407.0], [682.0, 1534.0], [659.0, 1534.0]]], "lines": ["無理", "してない？"]}, {"box": [213, 1126, 274, 1348], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22, "lines_coords": [[[250.0, 1129.0], [271.0, 1129.0], [271.0, 1317.0], [250.0, 1317.0]], [[215.0, 1129.0], [237.0, 1129.0], [239.0, 1339.0], [217.0, 1339.0]]], "l